measurements.description: Thirty-four flowers and one bud on three up to 72-cm inflorescences; sepals and petals lanceolate, light olive green, boldly striped light mahogany, dorsal sepal very hooded; lip slightly recurved distally, side lobes erect, cream overlaid light yellow distal half, side lobes striped brown, midlobe spotted mahogany, central mahogany stripe, keel cream spotted mahogany; column white overlaid yellow anterior, striped mahogany interior, anther cap cream, mahogany picotee; substance firm; texture matte.
